24
00:01:10,879 --> 00:01:16,079
Your favourite recipe is the classic British dish, bangers and mash.

25
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:20,520
It's easy to understand why mash potato is called mash,

26
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:24,359
but how did sausages come to be known as bangers?

27
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:25,840
Is it A?

28
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:29,200
Because bang is an old-fashioned word for pork,

29
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:33,799
B, because sausage-making machines used to make a banging noise,

30
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:38,680
