you can read more on Abna's website,

96
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:01,120
living the ancestral way.

97
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:04,920
And after all this talk of traditional Ghanaian food,

98
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:09,040
it's time for your question about a traditional British recipe,

99
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:12,480
bangers a mash or sausage and mashed potato.

100
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:15,080
Now you asked me about the name Banger,

101
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:18,640
