102
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:20,040
So was I right?

103
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:22,520
You were wrong, I'm afraid, Rob.

104
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:25,680
The name Banger started in World War I

105
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:29,480
when meat shortages resulted in sausages being made

106
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:34,480
using water that caused them to explode going bang when cooked.

107
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:38,240
Well, that's certainly one way to spice up your cooking.

108
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:40,960
Okay, let's recap the rest of the vocabulary

